Adjust National Focus Time

[h1]Supported Mods[/h1]
The Road to 56: [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3653420473]Adjust National Focus Time - The Road to 56[/url]
Old World Blues: [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3665129337]Adjust National Focus Time - Old World Blues[/url]
Millennium Dawn: [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?edit=true&id=3665125422]Adjust National Focus Time - Millennium Dawn
[/url]


[h1]Description[/h1]
Allows dynamic adjustment of the time required for all national focuses. The following options are available:
Reduce by 1 / 2 / 7 / 35 days
Increase by 1 / 2 / 7 / 35 days

These options appear in the form of Decisions.
Each option can be selected once per day.
Player only.
Only affects the national focus time of the currently played country.

[h1]Compatibility Notice[/h1]
This mod has compatibility issues with large overhaul mods (such as KR / KX) and may cause crashes. Please do not use them together.

If needed, please:
1. Use a dedicated compatibility version (if available)
or
2. Use the built-in tool included in this mod to generate a compatible version for the target mod

[b]Do not enable the unadapted version together with large overhaul mods.[/b]

